---
title: Coffee-Dukkah Rubbed Steak with Smash Potatoes and Chive Cream Sauce
description: Have you heard of dukkah? It's a delicious Egyptian condiment full of nuts, spices and herbs. Were also adding coffee to this rub for a sumptuous smoky crust on your steaks. There’s nothing about this dinner that isn't easy to love!
